title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1994-12-12
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Althea, Me & My Uncle*-> Maggie's Farm*, Candyman, Easy Answers, Bird Song

Set 2

Iko Iko, Childhood's End, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums**-> Space-> Standing On the Moon-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

* Weir on acoustic guitar. ** with Sikuru Adepoju
